title: Obama vows troops-bill veto, demands domestic spending hikes
text: President Obama will veto the annual defense policy bill, the White House said Wednesday as it escalated a clash over spending into a major war-time deadlock that threatens everything from troops' pay raises to warship building plans. Republican negotiators on Capitol Hill reached a deal Tuesday on the policy bill, ... ...
